          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1682411126725-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your<strong> cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Return the<strong> potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mash until smooth</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1663095724233-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1663095724233-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1663095724233-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1663095724233-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1663095724233-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meatballs are browned, remove the dish from the oven</p><p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>beef stock mix</strong> to the dish and gently stir everything together</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
